  "description": "All Echo frames: frame canvas 40x40px, transparent background. No outlines. No shading. No gradients. No dithering. Colors: body #FFA300, cheek patch #FF004D, crest #FFEC27, beak/feet #AB5236, eyes #1D2B53. Echo occupies approx x=6..33,y=6..36 within the 40x40 canvas. Cheek patch is always present as a 3x3 block at x=24..26,y=18..20. Eyes are two 2x2 blocks at x=14..15,y=16..17 and x=22..23,y=16..17 unless the frame specifies eyes closed. Happy: 8 frames, FPS=4, loop=false (play twice then return to idle). Crest raised: add 6 additional #FFEC27 pixels above head compared to idle in all frames. Frames 3-6: wings slightly open (add 2px on both sides at y=24..26 in #FFA300).",
